  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is the perfect mix of relaxation and luxury. Enjoy a warm, family welcome and incredible facilities. We can't get enough of the rooftop Jacuzzi where you can chill out next to the mountains. Rooms are spacious with private balconies looking out over the town or mountain. The village centre and lifts are a five-minute walk away but we prefer to jump on the free shuttle that runs all day at your beck and call.</p>]]></listingDescription>
